Sir, I am Mrs Absolutely Average working mother with two children and a
business to support and I spend discriminatingly as follows:
Shoes: Italian or French.
Washing machine: Swedish.
Dishwasher: German.
Car: German.
Clothes: 80 per cent Italian or French, usually from Japanese- owned
